f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"我讀BU，所以佢地本身就有個宗哲系，咁的當年屎忽痕reg左兩科黎讀，一科講islam，就講得幾公平，由10世紀既盛世講到現代陷入危機既野，讀完學到好多野，似教歷史仲多，而且佢分析宗教同政治之間既野係真心見識好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一科叫宗教與科學，但我讀完後覺得應該叫「宗教大撚曬」就岩，個講師係極端耶撚，不斷唱衰科學扭曲歷史，講到咩相對論日心說其實一早已經係聖經到有寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又成日話審判日要黎，次次上堂都係到唱聖歌，似入左邪教團體咁，所以無幾耐drop撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638fa6a79ee559c6b76de8f18cd943830cc2ad54","tid":2387873,"uid":200686,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:22:52.000Z","msg":"呢科超hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18942b973f4d01593a9ab2f8084576e6303a6816","tid":2387873,"uid":200686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e492daaf6f5ceae749ea524373e091d82ef5fd7","tid":2387873,"uid":87859,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9fa4f7b011aebc19ca252b32ed2ebb991b0d6a","tid":2387873,"uid":87859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6db5dccec15e548c9ebbfe124f2bda80b03e46ea","tid":2387873,"uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e36fa424d9a1b40595342afd80805c993e1820d4","tid":2387873,"uid":87859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56bf1e8498853dac37b9bd7fa79d7e04fdc6a7e5","tid":2387873,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:11:02.000Z","msg":"大學就有reg過2科關於宗教既野黎